  "tells": [
    "Common mistakes include pumping Wilhelt without enough sacrifice outlets, overcommitting to combat without protection, and ignoring graveyard hate.",
    "Unique interactions: Rooftop Storm\u2019s flying synergy is crucial for maximizing damage.",
    "Sacrifice outlets can target your own tokens for value, but watch out for \u201csacrifice\u201d hate like Rest in Peace or Leyline of the Void.",
    "Always track opponent\u2019s hand size and mana to time your pump correctly."
  ],
